member.summary:
Looks up a localized string similar to How to check your username in files:
1. Open Files (explorer.exe) 2. On the left side of Files, right click the "Downloads" button. 3. In the properties window, go to where it says "Location" 4. Next to "Location", it will say your username (Example: C:\Users\YOUR USERNAME\Downloads) 5. Next to where it says "Users\" is your username.
Enter that username into the textbox on the setup screen behind this message.
